Changelog
=========

0.5 (2015-02-13)
----------------

* Removed anylink and filer extensions from being autoloaded.
* Removed dependency on floppyforms.


0.2..0.4 (2015-01-22)
----------------

* General cleanups and bugfixes.


0.1 (2015-01-22)
----------------

* Initial release.


